Class DemoFrame

java.lang.Object

                      com.jgoodies.looks.demo.DemoFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public final class DemoFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame

Demonstrates how to use the jGoodies Looks. Therefore, it provides several panels, that comprise a variety of Swing widgets in different configurations.

Also, this frame contains examples for Swing misuse, that can be automatically corrected by ClearLook.

Author:
Karsten Lentzsch
